{"tid":948622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓LG Uplus力排眾議 公開挺華為","createTime":"2018-12-20T08:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T04:43:39.000Z","uid":25468,"like":4,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"27ac430805a2adc8436b86c2d623a0a3c8c9636a","tid":948622,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/12/19/realtime/5683622.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F12%2F19%2Frealtime%2F5683622.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=a47c4691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在以美國為首的西方國家抵制華為之際，南韓LG Uplus公開力挺這家中國電信設備龍頭，這家南韓最小的無線電信營運商19日駁斥美國宣稱華為設備構成國安威脅的說法。<br />\n<br />\nLG Uplus執行長河勳懷（Ha Hyun-hwoi）為該公司使用華為的產品辯護，表示華為的設備通過第三方檢驗，相信外部調查結果也無疑慮。在美、澳等國相繼禁用華為設、歐洲電信營運商也日漸戒慎恐懼之際，LG Uplus的力挺無異是對華為投下信任票。<br />\n<br />\n河勳懷說：「待明年調查結束後，你將有機會看到安全問題獲得完全解決。」「全球逾170個國家使用華為的設備，截至目前為止並未出現任何安全問題。」<br />\n<br />\nLG Uplus明年準備推出第五代無線服務（5G），欲與資金雄厚的SK電訊（SK Telecom）和國內電信龍頭韓國電信（KT）一較高下。LG Uplus仰賴華為的設備、以及三星電子、愛立信（Ericsson）和諾基亞（Nokia）的產品來運作該公司的網路。<br />\n<br />\n自本月初華為財務長孟晚舟因涉嫌違反美對伊朗貿易制裁、詐欺美國銀行等罪名在加拿大被捕以來，LG Uplus的這番表態無疑是對華為最強有力的支持之一。<br />\n<br />\n河勳懷表示，安全是整個產業的重要議題，但不應將全部矛頭指向華為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/12650/3546358\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F12650%2F3546358&d=JToigBLEqFuBXABKqoXuzIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=c77116eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/12650/3546358</a>"},{"pid":"b5eb4232a0ff7efd5a5140c9407c722c955a05fe","tid":948622,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:10:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf5eb1047f448260f8779472c94dfd77b966169b","tid":948622,"uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:28:56.000Z","msg":"lg<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a414777561d3bf9f0b59307cb6fe4a7ee9e193","tid":948622,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:35:45.000Z","msg":"華為啲野咁易壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Good Luck"},{"pid":"6ea9720bcf4a489522a1bffedd23bacd4f4ed948","tid":948622,"uid":25468,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"bf5eb1047f448260f8779472c94dfd77b966169b","tid":948622,"uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:28:56.000Z","msg":"lg<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:35:51.000Z","msg":"LG 如果堅持 , 應該真係會收皮"},{"pid":"71b6b8e7c77dcf42d3df5d997c340646aeedf645","tid":948622,"uid":50776,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:37:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾泡菜公司 宜家都冇人用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c74aaea3545f086321aad32f2ae613bf8817702","tid":948622,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71b6b8e7c77dcf42d3df5d997c340646aeedf645","tid":948622,"uid":50776,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:37:31.000Z","msg":"垃圾泡菜公司 宜家都冇人用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:41:06.000Z","msg":"講緊 5G  network 喎"},{"pid":"16f22cfc9c95a3d4d57e340ec0da7a4df0afe364","tid":948622,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:41:39.000Z","msg":"好好奇3UK仲會唔會繼續用"},{"pid":"411b2311affe38d51bc8e4fa2c1ec91112b55355","tid":948622,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T08:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859888de6cda6d36656da9b7191f2cf088cd4fe0","tid":948622,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ea9720bcf4a489522a1bffedd23